content:
Congratulations, you set up the basic version of Service Cloud Voice and configured the contact center. To enable more advanced features, complete these optional customizations.

**Customize Your Contact Center**

* Customize Amazon Connect for Voice:
	+ Customize Call Journeys with Amazon Connect Flows
	+ Configure Single Sign-On (SSO) with Amazon Connect
	+ Service Cloud Voice Additional AWS Services Add-on License
	+ Increase Amazon Service Quotas
	+ Reach Your Customers Using High-Volume Outbound Calls
* Customize Partner Telephony for Voice:
	+ Configure Single Sign-On (SSO) with Salesforce as the Identity Provider
	+ Customize Call Routing
		- Set Up Queue-Based Routing for Calls
		- Route Calls to Queues
		- Set Up Queues for Calls
		- Add a Queue in the Contact Center
		- Map Your Salesforce Queues to Telephony Provider Queues
* Manage Contact Center Queues in Salesforce and Your Telephony Provider Using Groups
* Configure Omni-Channel:
	+ Route Calls with Omni-Channel Flows
	+ Connect Your Flow to Your Voice Channel

**Customize the Agent Experience**

* Create the Voice Call Record Page
* Set Up the Service Console App for Service Cloud Voice
* Configure the Phone Book for Outbound Calls
* Respect Agent Capacity for Voice Calls (Beta)
* Add Screen Pops to Give Agents More Context about Conversations
* Sync Agent Presence Statuses Automatically
* Map Your Presence Statuses to Amazon Connect
* Grant Agents Access to View Agent Statuses When Transferring Calls
* Customize Call Controls and Voice Extensions
* Let Agents Pause and Resume Voice Call Recordings

**Customize the Supervisor Experience**

* Enable Omni Supervisor
* Enable the Default Actions on Omni Supervisor Tabs
* Show the Default Actions on Omni Supervisor Tabs
* Set Up Custom Actions on Omni Supervisor Tabs
* Change What Supervisors See in Omni Supervisor
* Show All Offline Agents in Omni Supervisor
* Create Custom Tabs for Omni Supervisor
* Add Omni Supervisor to the Service Console
* Enable Listen In for Supervisors

**Automate Your Contact Center with Artificial Intelligence**

* Sentiment Journey for Call Conversations
* Set Up Conversation Intelligence
* Set Up Work Summaries for Enhanced Messaging and Set Up Work Summaries for Voice Calls
title: Service Cloud Voice Customization
